---
// HowItWorks.astro - 4 steps: Sign up, Start Learning, Weekly Calls, Keep Growing
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        How It Works
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        A simple, proven process designed to accelerate your career growth in just a few months.
      </p>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-blue-600 mx-auto mt-6"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <!-- Step 1: Sign Up -->
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-200 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Sign Up</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Complete a quick application and schedule your initial strategy session.
            We'll assess your goals and create a personalized plan.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2: Start Learning -->
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-green-200 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Start Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Access curated resources, frameworks, and tools tailored to your specific career path.
            Begin implementing strategies immediately.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3: Weekly Calls -->
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-purple-200 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">3</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Weekly Calls</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Regular one-on-one sessions to track progress, overcome obstacles, and adjust your strategy.
            Get real-time feedback and guidance.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4: Keep Growing -->
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-orange-200 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-600">4</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Keep Growing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Continue building momentum with ongoing support, networking opportunities,
            and advanced strategies for long-term success.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <button
        onclick="document.getElementById('signup').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'})"
        class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
      >
        Start Your Transformation
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
